reviewText: You get a really good workout with this DVD.  I also purchased her Step Cardio Kickboxing, which is also awesome.
have many prior kcm videos.  this does not disappoint
Another great Kelly workout! I have 13 of her workout dvds . This is good for intermediate level fitness . She makes working out fun and effective!
Love this video! Love the sculpting video
Thiso came up when I searched for an advanced kickboxing dvd. This is not advanced at all. It's really low quality also.

My first time working out with Kelly DVD.  Glad I added this one to my collection, its a great workout for me. It contains 2 30 minutes workouts and options to customize. One workout is cardio boxing moves and the other workout is cardio using hand weights or dumbells for sculpting.
Love this video.  It is fun and a great workout in just 30 minutes.
